            class="- topic/topic concept/concept ">
		    <title class="- topic/title ">
			      <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">15.607</ph> Criteria for acceptance and negotiation of an unsolicited proposal.</title>
		    <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
			      <ol id="d946e13" class="- topic/ol ">
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d960e17" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            A favorable comprehensive evaluation of an unsolicited proposal does not, in itself, justify awarding a contract without providing for full and open competition. The agency point of contact shall return an unsolicited proposal to the offeror, citing reasons, when its substance-</p>
					          <ol id="d946e23" class="- topic/ol ">
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d960e27" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                Is available to the Government without restriction from another source;</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d960e36" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                Closely resembles a pending competitive acquisition requirement;</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d960e45" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(3)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                Does not relate to the activity’s mission; or</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d960e54" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(4)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                Does not demonstrate an innovative and unique method, approach, or concept, or is otherwise not deemed a meritorious proposal.</p>
						            </li>
					          </ol>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d960e65" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            The contracting officer may commence negotiations on a sole source basis only when-</p>
					          <ol id="d946e71" class="- topic/ol ">
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d960e75" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                An unsolicited proposal has received a favorable comprehensive evaluation;</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d960e84" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                A justification and approval has been obtained (see <xref href="FAR-i1119466.dita#i1119466"
                              base="i1119466"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">6.302-1</xref>(a)(2)(i) for research proposals or other appropriate provisions of <xref href="FAR-i1119434.dita#i1119434"
                              base="i1119434"
                              outputclass="fm:Subpart"
                              class="- topic/xref ">subpart  6.3</xref>, and <xref href="FAR-i1119771.dita#i1119771"
                              base="i1119771"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">6.303-2</xref>(c));</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d960e102" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(3)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                The agency technical office sponsoring the contract furnishes the necessary funds; and</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d960e111" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(4)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                The contracting officer has complied with the synopsis requirements of <xref href="FAR-i1120661.dita#i1120661"
                              base="i1120661"
                              outputclass="fm:Subpart"
                              class="- topic/xref ">subpart  5.2</xref>.</p>
						            </li>
					          </ol>
				        </li>
			      </ol>
